data.description: Looking for city living with a view.  Well don't miss this opportunity to feel like you live in the county but still live in the city, this is it.  This spacious 1600 sq ft home features a master bedroom with a full bath. The kitchen over looks the dinning room and has a 5 burner gas cook top, large living room that looks out onto an open field.  The family room is located on the lower level with plenty of room for TV watch, hanging out with friends maybe a pool table or anything else you can think of. Out side you will enjoy the large back yard and deck area.  If you looking for storage well look no more.  This home has a storage unit under the car port and a 10 ft. x 12 ft. building that is wired for electricity.  Use it for storage or as a work shop.  The choice is yours.
